About Me

Passionate about technical excellence in apparel development

I am a seasoned Technical Apparel Designer with 9 years of hands-on experience at Ha-Meem Group, one of Bangladesh's leading RMG companies. My journey began as a Pattern Technician, and through dedication and continuous skill development, I've evolved into a comprehensive technical designer.

My expertise spans the full spectrum of technical design: from creating first patterns through bulk production grading, conducting garment fit reviews on forms and in CLO3D, developing detailed tech packs, and providing technical advisory services to factories. I specialize in translating design concepts into manufacturable garments that meet exact specifications.

Currently pursuing a BSc in Textile Engineering at Sonargaon University while freelancing, I'm eager to contribute my skills to innovative brands and help shape the future of apparel design and production at a global level.
